sentence: where can i eat french food in the bay area ?
sentence-with-vars: where can i eat VARfood food in the VARregion ?
sql: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from RESTAURANT,GEOGRAPHIC,LOCATION where RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME=GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME and GEOGRAPHIC.REGION='bay area' and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='french' and RESTAURANT.ID=LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID
sql-with-vars: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from RESTAURANT,GEOGRAPHIC,LOCATION where RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME=GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME and GEOGRAPHIC.REGION='VARregion' and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='VARfood' and RESTAURANT.ID=LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID
